Van Breda is accused of hacking his family to death with an axe at De Zalze Estate outside Stellenbosch in JanuaryÂ 2015, killing his father, mother and older brother, and injuring his sister Marli. Throughout the trial, Van Breda maintained his innocence, saying his family was attacked by an axe-wielding intruder wearing a balaclava. He pleaded not guilty to charges of murder and defeating the ends of justice. -Afro Reporter